<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-5"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-5')">5</a>. So what does actually look like? A world-breaking object that is? Like what, literally crack the Earth in half? B.N.</div>
